metadata.description:
Single Point #01
One of the coloways in the Virtual Izakaya series.

In addition to the people who live, I think there is history and stories in the buildings and rusted pipes in the city. By concentrating and reconstructing those shots like a collage, I breathed new life into it. I call this "Single Point" and develop expressions that include the hopes and future of society, and sometimes anger and irony.
metadata.name: Single Point #01 - Virtual Izakaya
